posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Home is where the heart is and that is where we are located, in the heart of Elk River!', 'Our community offers so much for so little.', 'Come see all that Dove Tree has to offer including our one, two and three bedroom apartment homes.', 'You will be impressed with our impeccably maintained property and professional staff.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Adjoining Dining Room', 'And Living Room Area', '- High Speed Cable & Internet Ready', '- Private Balconies & Large Patios – Many With Brilliant Views!', '- In-Home Air Conditioning Unit', '- Centrally Located Laundry Facilities', '- Spacious & Open Kitchens', '- Entry Way Coat Closet', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Dove Tree participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Dove Tree', '1105 Lions Park Drive', 'Elk River, MN, 55330', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'B075ZdiLrAwY']
